cs351.project2.crossover

Class CrossMutateSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs351.project2.crossover.CrossMutateSelector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Job

    public class CrossMutateSelector
extends java.lang.Object
implements Job
    A CrossMutateSelector wraps around an existing Cross and Tribe object and provides an easy way to select members from the Tribe and perform crossover operations with them. This implementation should be thread-safe.
